long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Take on the ultimate platforming challenge in Boxel Rebound! Navigate your way through a world of blocks, spikes, and traps as you jump, dodge, and survive increasingly difficult levels. With smooth mechanics, a simple yet addictive design, and customizable levels, this game is a test of skill and endurance!

Why You Should Install Boxel Rebound:
📦 Engaging Gameplay: Experience precise platforming and enjoy the thrill of beating challenging levels.
🎨 Level Editor: Unleash your creativity and design your own levels to share with friends.
🌍 Endless Fun: Explore a variety of built-in levels or dive into custom user-made challenges.
🎮 Perfect for All Skill Levels: Start with simple levels and progress to insane difficulty for a real test.
🕹️ Instant Access: Play directly in your browser—no downloads or installs needed!
